Actually wait, I should extract mentions from just the body to avoid false positives from the Files line itself. The Files line contains file paths that get matched by FILE_MENTION_RE, but those are already in declared_files. So extracting from the full text would only be a problem if the FILE_MENTION_RE doesn't match something in the Files line but does match later.

